title: Perush ha-Riṭba ṿe-tosafot R. Yeshaʿyah de-Ṭrani ʿal masekhet Ḳidushin
creator: Yôm-Ṭôv Ben-Avrāhām Ašbîlî,
subject: Historische Drucke
source: Yôm-Ṭôv Ben-Avrāhām Ašbîlî,: Perush ha-Riṭba ṿe-tosafot R. Yeshaʿyah de-Ṭrani ʿal masekhet Ḳidushin  zeh sefer toldot adam, ḥidushe ha-me'orot ha-gedolim mi-masekhet Ḳidushin .... Berlin  Berlin 1715
alternative: zeh sefer toldot adam, ḥidushe ha-me'orot ha-gedolim mi-masekhet Ḳidushin ...
